                    settlement_id,
                    transaction_id, 
                    installment_id,
                    paid_date,
                    paid_value,
                    discount,
                    fees,
                    attachment
                ) VALUES (
                    $1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8
                ) RETURNING 
                settlement_id,
                    transaction_id, 
                    installment_id,
                    paid_date,
                    paid_value,
                    discount,
                    fees,
                    attachment,
                    created_at,
                    updated_at,
                    deleted_at
